Welcome Aboard!
Piedmont's transcontinental service is the culmination of five years of
unparalleled growth, In a period of sixty months, Piedmont has taken delivery
of two additional aircraft every three months and added a new destination
every other month.
This growth has been founded on standards of service that stress excellence
and quality. Our transcontinental service gives us a new opportunity to
demonstrate just what Piedmont can do. On behalf of the 13,000 men and
women of Piedmont. I want you to know we take a special pride in having
Sincerely.
